snippet: As it works to gain F.D.A. approval for its product, the genetic testing service 23andMe said it would release only ancestry information and raw data.
lead_paragraph: As it works to gain F.D.A. approval for its product, the genetic testing service 23andMe said it would release only ancestry information and raw data.

headline.main: Genetic Tester to Stop Providing Data on Health Risks
